  <Properties />
  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>Check the <em>CheckBox </em>and open <em>DropDown </em>of <em>ComboBox </em>and all items will be&nbsp;sorted in <em>DropDown</em>. Uncheck the <em>CheckBox</em>, open the <em>DropDown </em>and items will be not sorted.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>The Visual WebGui <em>ComboBox </em>contains <em>Sorted </em>property that indicates whether the items in the combo box are sorted.</p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
</Data>
